\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Pita t…ôm…ôte naoa u.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm kotat…®g ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n e profens m…®n r…ôha Pontas, ne Kalesia, ne Kapetosia, ne Esia, ne Pitnia (1 Pita 1:1). Roiu kat…ôn n…ôrg…® n…ôpt…ôn m…®n …ôh m…ôm…ô Turke.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* E nian …ôh, et…ôm-iasol r…ôha Rom, n…ôrg…®n u Nero, t…ôm…ôr…ôk…®n p…®k nim…ôfak. T…ômoh nim…ôfak m…®n neen kot…®m…®s, k…ôn moh neen. Ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn toh Pita.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Pita tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha i…ôfak m…®n it…ôm kotat…®g e n…ôrat…ôn. In tolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…ôtul …ôskas…®k e r…ôhalat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn k…ôn moatol nat kit it…ôm t…ôw…®r, nat …ôpnap…®n n…ôrat…ôn tatuwa.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pita t…ôm…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm ilat  
\m
\v 1 Io Pita, io aposol kit r…ôha Iesu Kristo. Iat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat net…ôm r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm n…ôkotat…®g ik…®n m…®n rafin …ôp…ôh e profens m…®n u Pontas, ne Kalesia, ne Kapatosia, ne Esia, ne Pitinia. Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s it…ômat, k…ôn imat…ômat ik…®n s…ôn…ôm…ô n…ôtueint…ôn u, it…ômat iap…®sp…®s m…®n …ôm u ik…®n-u.  
\v 2 Tata Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun it…ômat m…ôto-inu, aup…ôn aup…ôn ag…®n, t…ômol r…ôhan nalp…ôkau…ôn m…ôl…ôh…ôu, k…ôn in t…®n…®tun r…ôk…®s suat…®p m…®n rafin r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat. K…ôn Narm…®n R…ôhan tatol it…ômat nakot…ôtul p…®s…®n kasim m…ôm…ô, n…ôkotol n…ôwia Iesu Kristo, k…ôn n…®tan taikuas et…ômat e nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhat…ômat.\f + \fr 1:2 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, Uhg…®n ‚Äút…ômorautin n…®ta Iesu etat‚Äù u n…®p…ôt…®n m…ôm…ô t…ôtaikuas et…ômat o nol…ôn rat m…®n. Afin m…®n e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u ‚Äút…ôtorautin n…®tan‚Äù ne ‚Äún…®tan taikuas e net…ômim‚Äù: Lev 14:6-7; Sam 51:7; Eks 24:5-8; Hip 9:19; 1 Jon 1:7.\f*  
\p P…ôs Uhg…®n otawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn ne n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn tep…ôt k…ôm it…ômat.   
\s1 Ot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n o nalp…ôkau…ôn r…ôhan  
\p
\v 3 !P…ôs kot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n it…ôm in Uhg…®n ne Tata r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu Kristo r…ôhatat! E nas…ôkitun…ôn asol r…ôhan, in t…ômol m…ôm…ô kitat kotaiir-p…ôn e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn wi, k…ôn moat…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhatat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn lan. Tatuwa min-n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu Iesu Kristo t…ôm…ômeg…ôh m…®n e r…ôhan n…®m…®s…ôn.  
\v 4 K…ôn e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn wi u, kitat okotos nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n …ôp…ôh e nego e neai it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu p…®s…®n m…ôm…ô r…ôhatat. K…ôn nat u okol t…ôs…ômn…ôm…®t…ôn, k…ôn okol t…ôsamk…®m…®k…ôn, k…ôn okol r…ôhan n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn t…ôs…®k…ô…ôn.\x - \xo 1:4 \xt Kol 1:12 \x*  
\v 5 E nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôtulos…®g-in it…ômat m…ôtoarus-pa in otosmeg…ôh it…ômat, k…ôn Uhg…®n otol …ôp r…ôhan nosmeg…ôh…ôn e namnun nian.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Jon 10:28; 17:11 \x*   
\p
\v 6 N…®kit…ômat t…ôtagien o nat u, nat …ôpnap…®n ok…ôm…ô nian i…ôk…®s p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n koatuwa pap e r…ôhat…ômat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. M…ôto koatuwa o nian …ôku…ôk…®r …ôm.\x - \xo 1:6 \xt Jem 1:2; 1 Pita 5:10 \x*  
\v 7 Nian i…ôk…®s m…®n …ôh moatuwa m…ôm…ô okot…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô it…ômat nakotahat…ôt…ô pahrien. Iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t, in nat kit it…ôm n…®g…ôm tatus m…ôtaf…ôl r…ôk…®s in rat m…®n lan. K…ôn nian i…ôk…®s m…®n …ôh kotahmen e n…®g…ôm it…ôm tatus r…ôhat…ômat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn m…ôtaf…ôl r…ôk…®s in rat m…®n lan. Iaen u kol, in nat t…ôw…®r, m…ôto ot…ôpan…®k…ô m…®n nian kit. M…ôto r…ôhat…ômat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, in nat t…ôw…®r tapr…ôk…®s-in iaen u kol. K…ôn o r…ôhat…ômat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, Uhg…®n ot…ônwiwi it…ômat, m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…®t…ômat, mos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn asol k…ôm it…ômat e nian Iesu Kristo otuwa met-ar…ôpa lan.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Prov 17:3; Sek 13:9; Mal 3:3; Jem 1:3 \x*  
\v 8 Nat …ôpnap…®n n…ôm…ôsot…ôplan pap…ôn Iesu Kristo, m…ôto nakoatolkeike. K…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n n…ôsotehm…ôn u-roiu, m…ôto nakotahat…ôt…ô lan. K…ôn n…®kit…ômat t…ôm…ôr m…ôrioah e nagien…ôn it…ôm in t…ôw…®r ag…®n-…ôh tapr…ôk…®s, k…ôn okol suah kit t…ôs…ôn…ôn n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôha nagien…ôn …ôh.\x - \xo 1:8 \xt Jon 20:29; 2 Kor 5:7 \x*  
\v 9 N…®kit…ômat t…ôtagien n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu it…ômat noatos nat u it…ôm nakotahat…ôt…ô lan, inu m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otosmeg…ôh r…ôhat…ômat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.   
\p
\v 10 Suat…®p r…ôha Uhg…®n o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ômim lan, in nat kit it…ôm ien m…®n aup…ôn k…ômotolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô okot…®tun tuw…®n t…ôhm…®n m…®n, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan k…ômotafin kateg…ôs-in w…®r n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…®n lan. K…ôn ilat k…ômoat…ôghat-in n…ôw…®r…ôn u it…ôm otuwa k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt Mat 13:16-17 \x*  
\v 11 Narm…®n r…ôha Kristo t…ôm…ôtat…®g ilat min, k…ôn mat…ôghat k…ôm ilat, k…ôn aup…ôn ik…®n mat…ôn-iar…ôp nahm…ô…ôn it…ôm okotuwa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Iesu, k…ôn uaris…®g lan e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn asol r…ôhan. M…ôto ien m…®n k…ômotalkut o n…®tun…ôn suat…®p it…ôm nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh okotuwa lan, ne r…ôhalat nian …ôtuat…®p.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Sam 22; Aes 53; Luk 24:26-27 \x*  
\v 12 Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôp k…ôm ien m…®n m…ôm…ô, n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm ilat k…ômoat…ôn, k…ôm…ôsot…ôghat-in…ôn nian it…ôm ilat k…ômotat…®g lan, m…ôto k…ômot…ôghat-in …ôm nian r…ôhatat. K…ôn roiu, net…ômim k…®not…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn e nego e neai. K…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u kot…ôw…®r ag…®n m…ôm…ô nagelo m…®n, ilat m…®n kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan k…ôn mot…®tun nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm k…ômotuwa.   
\s1 Nol…ôn r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p  
\p
\v 13 Tol n…ôhlan, n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motol r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôtul mat…®p o nol…ôn w…ôk, k…ôn mot…ôg…ôtun w…®r r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn. Ot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn e n…ôw…®r…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n otawte-in k…ôm it…ômat nian Iesu Kristo otuwa m…®n.  
\v 14 Otol n…ôwia Uhg…®n tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô n…®sualk…ôl…ôh it…ôm kot…ôw…®r koatol n…ôwia tata m…®n. Aup…ôn ik…®n, it…ômat n…ôm…ôsot…®tun…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn n…ômoatol nol…ôn rat m…®n it…ôm n…®kit…ômat …ôm tolkeike. M…ôto roiu, ot…ôseg…ôhan-in…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…®n …ôh okotiuw r…ôk…®s m…®n it…ômat.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Rom 12:2; Efes 2:3; 4:17-18 \x*  
\v 15 Uhg…®n u it…ôm t…ômaun-in it…ômat, in tasim m…ôtuat…®p. K…ôn e nol…ôn …ôh in…ôh, it…ômat m…®n on…ôkot…ôk…ôike motasim mot…ôtuat…®p e nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm n…ôkoatol.  
\v 16 N…ôkot…ôk…ôike motol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôkot…ôk…ôike motasim mot…ôtuat…®p m…ôto-inu Io ekasim m…ôtuat…®p.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:16 \xt Lev 11:44,45; 19:2; 20:7\x*   
\p
\v 17 It…ômat nakot…ôtap…ôh-in nasitu…ôn o Uhg…®n u tahmen m…ôm…ô in r…ôhat…ômat Tata, m…ôto on…ôk…ôsotaluin…ôn m…ôm…ô nian Uhg…®n t…ôtakil nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha net…ômim, in tatol …ôm e nol…ôn it…ôm tahmen-ahmen …ôm. Tol n…ôhlan, nian nakot…ômeg…ôh …ôh e n…ôtueint…ôn u, on…ôkot…ôg…®n mot…®siai-in Uhg…®n e nol…ôn m…®n r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôn otol nol…ôn t…ôw…®r tahmen m…ôm…ô it…ômat iap…®sp…®s m…®n …ôm e n…ôtueint…ôn u.\x - \xo 1:17 \xt Rom 2:11; Nol ∆èp…ôn 2:23 \x*  
\v 18 N…ôkot…ôk…ôike motol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu it…ômat n…ômot…®tun r…ôk…®s nat keike it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôtou r…ôk…®s it…ômat lan. Ot…ôt…ôl…®g-in-tu nol…ôn r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat aup…ôn it…ôm n…®p…ôt…®n t…®k…ô u t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn o t…®p…®t…ômat m…®n. M…ôto Uhg…®n t…ôm…®k…®s r…ôk…®s it…ômat e nol…ôn rat …ôh. K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsos-n…ômt…®n…ôn r…ôhat…ômat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn e nat kit r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn it…ôm ot…ôpan…®k…ô, tahmen e silfa ne iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t,\fig |alt="hand pierced" src="HK00322B.TIF" size="col" loc="1Pe 1:18-19" ref="1 Pita 1:18" \fig*  
\v 19 m…ôto in t…ômos-n…ômt…®n it…ômat e n…®ta Kristo it…ôm in nat keike t…ôw…®r p…®k ag…®n. Kristo in tahmen e n…ôt…® sipsip w…®r it…ôm n…®m…®s…ôn o n…ôrat…ôn t…®k…ô ag…®n lan.\f + \fr 1:19 \ft E nian r…ôha Oltesteman, net…ômim k…ômotol sakrifais k…ôm Uhg…®n o t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n e n…ôt…® sipsip m…®n it…ôm n…ôrat…ôn t…®k…ô lan. Afin e Eks 12:5.\f*\x - \xo 1:19 \xt W…ôk 20:28; Hip 9:12-14 \x*  
\v 20 Aup…ôn aup…ôn ag…®n, nian Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsol…ôn …ôh n…ôtueint…ôn u, t…ôm…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s Kristo m…ôm…ô otol w…ôk …ôh. M…ôto roiu iu…ôhk…®r o namnun nian, Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôp in, m…ôm…ô otuwa masitu et…ômat.\x - \xo 1:20 \xt 2 Tim 1:9-10 \x*  
\v 21 O nat…®mnat it…ôm Iesu t…ômol, it…ômat nakotahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n, it…ôm t…ômosmeg…ôh Iesu Kristo e n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr in mos-ip…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn it…ôm t…ôhag-…ôhag ne n…®siaii…ôn k…ôm in. K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, nakotahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n, k…ôn moat…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn lan.\x - \xo 1:21 \xt Jon 14:6; Rom 5:1-2 \x*   
\p
\v 22 N…ômotaikuas e r…ôhat…ômat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn t…®nuwa m…®nuwiwi m…®n r…ôk…®s m…ôto-inu n…ômot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha n…®pahrien…ôn. K…ôn o nat…®mnat m…®n u, nakotos nolkeike…ôn pahrien tatuw…®n ot…ômat m…®n neen. K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, otolkeike p…®k it…ômat m…®n e n…®kin pahrien.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Jon 13:34; Rom 12:10 \x*  
\v 23 Otol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, n…ômotaiir wi r…ôk…®s m…®n, k…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn wi r…ôhat…ômat t…ôm…ôs…®s…®-p…ôn…ôn o net…ômim it…ôm ilat rafin ok…ôpanot…®m…®s. M…ôto n…ômeg…ôh…ôn wi u r…ôhat…ômat in ot…ôtat…®g namnun t…®k…ô m…ôto-inu t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn kit it…ôm tat…ômeg…ôh m…ôtat…®g namnun t…®k…ô, inu n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 24 Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúNet…ômim rafin kotahmen e ma k…®ras,  
\q1 k…ôn n…ôw…®r…ôn rafin r…ôhalat tahmen …ôm e n…ôgu…®-n…®g …ôp…ôh e n…®kinat.  
\q1 Ma k…®ras …ôh t…ôtauke, k…ôn n…ôgu…®n m…®n koat…®sas,   
\q1
\v 25 m…ôto n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôtat…®g lil…®n namnun t…®k…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:25 \xt Aes 40:6-8\x*  
\m K…ôn inu n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r it…ôm net…ômim k…ômot…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat.   
\c 2  
\m
\v 1 M…ôto-inu o n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh, ot…ôrakin nol…ôn m…®n u kotiet r…ôk…®s e r…ôhat…ômat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn: nol…ôn rafin r…ôha net…ôhau…ôn net…ômim k…ôn matol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm ilat; nol…ôn rafin r…ôha neiu…ô…ôn; nol…ôn r…ôha net…ôm koat…ôn p…®k …ôm nat, m…ôto k…ôsotol…ôn; nol…ôn r…ôha netet…ôn; nol…ôn rafin r…ôha n…ôn rat…ôn net…ômim.\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Efes 4:22; Jem 1:21 \x*  
\v 2-3 It…ômat n…ômot…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômol t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat. Tahmen-p…ôn m…ôm…ô n…ômotun asg…ôw…®n noa n…®g it…ôm t…ôtehen.\x - \xo 2:2-3 \xt Sam 34:8\x* K…ôn roiu n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motuwa kahmen e n…®sualk…ôl…ôh m…ôtm…ôt…®g it…ôm kotas…ôk o n…ôm…ôh…ôn. It…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike kolkeike p…®k nagw…ôn…ôn ne n…ôn…®m…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p m…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nakotagw…ôn n…®kit…ômat lan. K…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh okotol nakotep…ôt e r…ôhat…ômat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômosmeg…ôh it…ômat lan.\x - \xo 2:2-3 \xt Sam 34:8 \x*   
\s1 K…ôpiel meg…ôh e nim…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n  
\p
\v 4 Uhg…®n tolkeike m…ôm…ô otil…ôk…®n r…ôhan kit nim…ô e kitat net…ômim, k…ôn t…ôm…®t…ôpun K…ôpiel kit it…ôm net…ômim k…ômotap…ôs, m…ôto in k…ôpiel keike tat…ômeg…ôh m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôtuoun nim…ô lan. K…ôn nian nakotuwa o k…ôpiel u Kristo e suat…®p r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn,  
\v 5 it…ômat m…®n, n…ôkotahmen e k…ôpiel meg…ôh m…®n it…ôm Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n tatos it…ômat matil…ôk…®n Nim…ô lan R…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn it…ômat pris asim m…®n, it…ôm nakoatos-ip…ôn sakrifais m…®n k…ôm Uhg…®n it…ôm n…®kin t…ôtagien ron m…ôto-inu o nat…®mnat it…ôm Iesu Kristo t…ômol.\x - \xo 2:5 \xt Rom 12:1; Efes 2:21-22; Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:6\x*  
\v 6 Tahmen-p…ôn e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn mihin m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúOt…ôplan-tu. Iakat…ôl…ôh…ôu k…ôpiel …ôp…ôh Jerusalem,\f + \fr 2:6 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSaeon,‚Äù n…ôrg…®n kit m…®n r…ôha Jerusalem.\f*  
\q1 inu k…ôpiel keike p…®k ag…®n it…ôm io em…®t…ôpun,  
\q1 k…ôpiel u in r…ôha n…ôtuoun…ôn nim…ô,  
\q1 k…ôn et…ômim it…ôm otahat…ôt…ô lan,  
\q1 in ot…ôsaul…®s…ôn.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Aes 28:16; Efes 2:20\x*   
\m
\v 7 K…ôpiel u in nat keike k…ôm it…ômat it…ôm nakoatahat…ôt…ô lan. M…ôto k…ôm net…ômim it…ôm k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan, k…ôpiel u in tahmen-p…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn u e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…ôpiel u it…ôm net…ôm r…ôha nil…ôk…®n…ôn nim…ô k…ômot…ôrakin,  
\q1 m…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômol tuwa k…ôpiel it…ôm in r…ôha n…ôtuoun…ôn nim…ô,‚Äù\x - \xo 2:7 \xt Sam 118:22\x*   
\m
\v 8 k…ôn Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…ôpiel u tatol net…ômim koat…®l…ôs p…®k…ôn,  
\q1 k…ôn in k…ôpiel it…ôm tatol m…ôm…ô net…ômim kotiet katorin.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:8 \xt Aes 8:14\x*  
\m Ilat koat…®l…ôs p…®k…ôn k…ôpiel u m…ôto-inu koat…ôht n…ôwia n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn inu nalp…ôkau…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol olat.   
